                "Neutron detection efficiency was determined to be",
                "   (50.81+-0.15)%"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Surrogate method was used. Reaction",
                "   n + 241Pu -> 242Pu* -> FL + FH + nu*N",
                "was replaced by reaction",
                "   a + 242Pu -> 242Pu* + a' -> FL + FH + nu*N",
                "    (a' -> inelastically scattered alpha particle)",
                "assuming Bohr independence hypothesis"
              ]
            }
